; Regression test for issue #1585: --comm-as-payee (-x) is unrecognized (BZ#513)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1585

2024/01/01 Test Payee
    Expenses:Food    10 USD
    Assets:Cash     -10 USD

test reg --comm-as-payee -> 1
__ERROR__
Error: Illegal option --comm-as-payee
end test

test reg -x -> 1
__ERROR__
Error: Illegal option -x
end test
